Hi OPC!

I’m Edward, an FEU alum and currently working in an agency that handles multiple brands.
We’re currently looking for nano KOLs on TikTok who love coffee ☕ and would be interested in an x-deal collaboration for an exciting university invasion campaign!

Requirements:
🔹 1k+ TikTok followers
🔹 Willing to post 1 TikTok content in exchange for a PR kit
If you’re interested, send me a message so we can chat and work out the details.
Thanks, and hope to collaborate with you soon!
